    "content": {
      "rendered": "<p><a href=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/Instgram-Video-Interviews-Facebook.jpg\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignright size-medium wp-image-17486\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/Instgram-Video-Interviews-Facebook-300x300.jpg?resize=300%2C300\" alt=\"Instgram Video Interviews Facebook\" width=\"300\" height=\"300\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/Instgram-Video-Interviews-Facebook.jpg?resize=300%2C300&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/Instgram-Video-Interviews-Facebook.jpg?resize=150%2C150&amp;ssl=1 150w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/Instgram-Video-Interviews-Facebook.jpg?resize=200%2C200&amp;ssl=1 200w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/Instgram-Video-Interviews-Facebook.jpg?resize=75%2C75&amp;ssl=1 75w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/Instgram-Video-Interviews-Facebook.jpg?w=500&amp;ssl=1 500w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px\" /></a>15-second video interviews are the new elevator pitch. In a world where attention spans are waning, the ability to communicate a message succinctly and on camera is a very valuable skill. While a few individuals succeeded in just one take, most needed two or three takes. Getting your point across verbally in 15 seconds while the camera is recording is much harder than it looks! That said, this year&#8217;s Nonprofit Technology Conference <strong>(<a href=\"https://storify.com/nonprofitorgs\" target=\"_blank\">view on Storify</a>)</strong> produced sixteen Instagram videos in response to the question: <em>What is your number one piece of nonprofit technology advice?</em></p>\n<h2><strong><br />\n1. Mona Cade</strong>\u00f1a of <a href=\"http://ejusa.org/\" target=\"_blank\">Equal Justice USA</a></h2>\n<blockquote class=\"instagram-media\" style=\"background: #FFF; border: 0; border-radius: 3px; box-shadow: 0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width: 658px; padding: 0; width: calc(100% - 2px);\" data-instgrm-captioned=\"\" data-instgrm-version=\"4\">\n<div style=\"padding: 8px;\">\n<div style=\"background: #F8F8F8; line-height: 0; margin-top: 40px; padding: 50% 0; text-align: center; width: 100%;\"></div>\n<p style=\"margin: 8px 0 0 0; padding: 0 4px;\"><a style=\"color: #000; font-family: Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: 17px; text-decoration: none; word-wrap: break-word;\" href=\"https://instagram.com/p/z5PXLLwugA/\" target=\"_top\">#15NTC Mona Cadena (@grrlinthecity) of Equal Justice USA</a></p>\n<p style=\"color: #c9c8cd; font-family: Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 17px; margin-bottom: 0; margin-top: 8px; overflow: hidden; padding: 8px 0 7px; text-align: center; text-overflow: ellipsis; white-space: nowrap;\">A video posted by Nonprofit Organizations (@nonprofitorgs) on <time style=\"font-family: Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 17px;\" datetime=\"2015-03-06T17:19:04+00:00\">Mar 6, 2015 at 9:19am PST</time></p>\n</div>\n</blockquote>\n<p><script src=\"//platform.instagram.com/en_US/embeds.js\" async=\"\" defer=\"defer\"></script></p>\n<h2><strong><br />\n 2. Helene Kahn\u00a0of <a href=\"http://www1.networkforgood.org/\" target=\"_blank\">Network for Good</a></strong></h2>\n<blockquote class=\"instagram-media\" style=\"background: #FFF; border: 0; border-radius: 3px; box-shadow: 0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width: 658px; padding: 0; width: calc(100% - 2px);\" data-instgrm-captioned=\"\" data-instgrm-version=\"4\">\n<div style=\"padding: 8px;\">\n<div style=\"background: #F8F8F8; line-height: 0; margin-top: 40px; padding: 50% 0; text-align: center; width: 100%;\"></div>\n<p>\u00a0 <a style=\"color: #000; font-family: Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: 17px; text-decoration: none; word-wrap: break-word;\" href=\"https://instagram.com/p/z5VaHDQuqU/\" target=\"_top\">Helene Kahn (@helenemaekahn) of @NetworkForGood</a> \u00a0 A video posted by Nonprofit Organizations (@nonprofitorgs) on <time style=\"font-family: Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 17px;\" datetime=\"2015-03-06T18:11:54+00:00\">Mar 6, 2015 at 10:11am PST</time>\n</div>\n</blockquote>\n<p><script src=\"//platform.instagram.com/en_US/embeds.js\" async=\"\" defer=\"defer\"></script></p>\n<h2><strong><br />\n3. Claire Kerr of <a href=\"http://www.frontstream.com/\" target=\"_blank\">FrontStream</a></strong></h2>\n<blockquote class=\"instagram-media\" style=\"background: #FFF; border: 0; border-radius: 3px; box-shadow: 0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width: 658px; padding: 0; width: calc(100% - 2px);\" data-instgrm-captioned=\"\" data-instgrm-version=\"4\">\n<div style=\"padding: 8px;\">\n<div style=\"background: #F8F8F8; line-height: 0; margin-top: 40px; padding: 50% 0; text-align: center; width: 100%;\"></div>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><a style=\"color: #000; font-family: Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: 17px; text-decoration: none; word-wrap: break-word;\" href=\"https://instagram.com/p/z5ItsqwukN/\" target=\"_top\">#15NTC Claire Kerr (@snotforprofit) of FrontStream</a></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>A video posted by Nonprofit Organizations (@nonprofitorgs) on <time style=\"font-family: Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 17px;\" datetime=\"2015-03-06T16:20:59+00:00\">Mar 6, 2015 at 8:20am PST</time></p>\n</div>\n</blockquote>\n<h2><script src=\"//platform.instagram.com/en_US/embeds.js\" async=\"\" defer=\"defer\" type=\"text/javascript\"></script></h2>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<h2>4.\u00a0<span data-reactid=\".5i.0.1.0.1.0.0.1.0.0.0:0.1.2:1.$text0:0:$text1:0\">Mark Horvath of\u00a0<a href=\"http://invisiblepeople.tv/blog/\" target=\"_blank\">Invisible People</a></span></h2>\n<blockquote class=\"instagram-media\" style=\"background: #FFF; border: 0; border-radius: 3px; box-shadow: 0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width: 658px; padding: 0; width: calc(100% - 2px);\" data-instgrm-captioned=\"\" data-instgrm-version=\"4\">\n<div style=\"padding: 8px;\">\n<div style=\"background: #F8F8F8; line-height: 0; margin-top: 40px; padding: 50% 0; text-align: center; width: 100%;\"></div>\n<p><a style=\"color: #000; font-family: Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: 17px; text-decoration: none; word-wrap: break-word;\" href=\"https://instagram.com/p/z5Hdl7Quhh/\" target=\"_top\">#15NTC Mark Horvath of @InvisiblePeople</a> A video posted by Nonprofit Organizations (@nonprofitorgs) on <time style=\"font-family: Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 17px;\" datetime=\"2015-03-06T16:10:02+00:00\">Mar 6, 2015 at 8:10am PST</time>\n</div>\n</blockquote>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<h2>5. Gwen Nguyen of <a href=\"https://www.indiegogo.com/\" target=\"_blank\">Indiegogo</a></h2>\n<blockquote class=\"instagram-media\" style=\"background: #FFF; border: 0; border-radius: 3px; box-shadow: 0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width: 658px; padding: 0; width: calc(100% - 2px);\" data-instgrm-captioned=\"\" data-instgrm-version=\"4\">\n<div style=\"padding: 8px;\">\n<div style=\"background: #F8F8F8; line-height: 0; margin-top: 40px; padding: 50% 0; text-align: center; width: 100%;\"></div>\n<p><a style=\"color: #000; font-family: Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: 17px; text-decoration: none; word-wrap: break-word;\" href=\"https://instagram.com/p/z5PzK9Qugr/\" target=\"_top\">#15NTC Gwen Nguyen (@unguyen) of @Indiegogo</a> A video posted by Nonprofit Organizations (@nonprofitorgs) on <time style=\"font-family: Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 17px;\" datetime=\"2015-03-06T17:22:53+00:00\">Mar 6, 2015 at 9:22am PST</time>\n</div>\n</blockquote>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<h2><script src=\"//platform.instagram.com/en_US/embeds.js\" async=\"\" defer=\"defer\"></script></h2>\n<h2>6. Ash Shepherd of <a href=\"http://www.nten.org/\" target=\"_blank\">NTEN</a></h2>\n<blockquote class=\"instagram-media\" style=\"background: #FFF; border: 0; border-radius: 3px; box-shadow: 0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width: 658px; padding: 0; width: calc(100% - 2px);\" data-instgrm-captioned=\"\" data-instgrm-version=\"4\">\n<div style=\"padding: 8px;\">\n<div style=\"background: #F8F8F8; line-height: 0; margin-top: 40px; padding: 50% 0; text-align: center; width: 100%;\"></div>\n<p><a style=\"color: #000; font-family: Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: 17px; text-decoration: none; word-wrap: break-word;\" href=\"https://instagram.com/p/z48ENzQutw/\" target=\"_top\">Ash Shepherd of @NTENorg</a> A video posted by Nonprofit Organizations (@nonprofitorgs) on <time style=\"font-family: Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 17px;\" datetime=\"2015-03-06T14:30:27+00:00\">Mar 6, 2015 at 6:30am PST</time></p>\n</div>\n</blockquote>\n<p><script src=\"//platform.instagram.com/en_US/embeds.js\" async=\"\" defer=\"defer\"></script></p>\n<h1 style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://instagram.com/nonprofitorgs/\" target=\"_blank\">View All 16 Instagram Videos</a></h1>\n<hr />\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17px;\"><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; font-weight: bold;\"><em>Mobile for Good: A How-To Fundraising Guide for Nonprofits</em></span></span></strong></h2>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.amazon.com/Mobile-Good-How--Fundraising-Nonprofits/dp/0071825460\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignleft wp-image-16024\" style=\"margin: 10px; border: 1px solid black;\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/05/mobile-for-good-look-inside.jpg?resize=99%2C150\" alt=\"mobile for good look inside\" width=\"99\" height=\"150\" /></a>Based on more than 20 years of experience and 25,000+ hours spent utilizing mobile and social media, <a href=\"http://www.amazon.com/Mobile-Good-How--Fundraising-Nonprofits/dp/0071825460\"><em><strong>Mobile for Good: A How-To Fundraising Guide for Nonprofits</strong></em></a> is a comprehensive 256-page book packed with more than 500 best practices. Written on the premise that all communications and fundraising are now mobile and social, Mobile for Good is a step-by-step how-to guide for writing, implementing, and maintaining a mobile and social fundraising strategy for your nonprofit.</p>\n",
